{"tid":2286128,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Media Research Center 力証偽善美媒","createTime":"2020-11-14T16:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T20:17:08.000Z","uid":12929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4329ddd7b2e8f9dd73b3c25fcff81c88e2885e","tid":2286128,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PJzhEaFYsfGm7kd5Dzk8_4AGjPQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VJ6V2VS6LNBKXDLM5CSHPUJKTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPJzhEaFYsfGm7kd5Dzk8_4AGjPQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVJ6V2VS6LNBKXDLM5CSHPUJKTM.jpg&h=ceda24b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n共和黨保守派傳媒監察組織「美國傳媒研究中心」（Media Research Center）將主流傳媒的做法，與20年前報道大選的方式作對比，更將相關的報道剪輯成短片，發現當時民主黨候選人戈爾和特朗普受到的待遇截然不同。該機構將有關片段上載Twitter分享，並配上「自由開明的傳媒現在譏笑特朗普拒絕承認落敗，但它們在2000年為戈爾慶祝，甚至公開地宣稱他勝出」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201114/J37PJPE5LNFDTGXV3LJ3HQV25M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201114%2FJ37PJPE5LNFDTGXV3LJ3HQV25M%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BM22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=49bacefc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201114%2FJ37PJPE5LNFDTGXV3LJ3HQV25M%2F&h=a5ef3d86\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201114/J37PJPE5LNFDTGXV3LJ3HQV25M/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/theMRC/status/1327322337054580736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FtheMRC%2Fstatus%2F1327322337054580736&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BM22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=62f8e492\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FtheMRC%2Fstatus%2F1327322337054580736&h=5d126b88\" target=\"_